<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>雨；雨水：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>in the rain</strong>
冒雨；在雨中</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>It looks like rain</strong>.
